---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Still">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-32 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <section class="py-24 bg-surface flex-grow">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <header class="mb-16">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display text-primary leading-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant opacity-70">Last Updated: May 2026</p>
        </header>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-on-surface-variant space-y-12">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-primary mb-4 border-b border-outline-variant pb-2">1. Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              At Still Studio, we treat your digital presence with the same reverence as a physical heirloom. We believe that luxury and privacy are inextricably linked. This policy outlines our rigorous standards for collecting, protecting, and managing the data of our clients and their esteemed guests.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-primary mb-4 border-b border-outline-variant pb-2">2. Data We Collect</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">To provide a seamless "Digital Concierge" experience, we collect specific information:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Client Data:</strong> Personal identifiers and billing details required to fulfill your bespoke commission.</li>
              <li><strong>Guest Data:</strong> Names, RSVP status, dietary requirements, and itinerary preferences shared via your portal.</li>
              <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Standard server logs and secure cookies used solely to optimize performance and protect against unauthorized access.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-primary mb-4 border-b border-outline-variant pb-2">3. Purpose and Guest Handling</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Data is collected exclusively to facilitate your event. We do not sell, trade, or share guest or client information with third-party marketers. Your guest list is treated with the highest level of confidentiality and remains your property.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-primary mb-4 border-b border-outline-variant pb-2">4. GDPR & Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">In accordance with global privacy standards, including GDPR, every individual has the right to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Access and receive a copy of their personal data.</li>
              <li>Request the immediate rectification or erasure of their information.</li>
              <li>Withdraw consent for data processing at any time.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-primary mb-4 border-b border-outline-variant pb-2">5. Data Retention & Archiving</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Active guest portals are maintained throughout your event cycle. Following your celebration, we provide a "Digital Heirloom" archive for your records. All active guest data is purged from our primary servers 12 months post-event unless otherwise directed.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-primary mb-4 border-b border-outline-variant pb-2">6. Contact for Inquiries</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              For all data requests, privacy questions, or to exercise your rights, please contact our studio directly at <strong class="text-primary">privacy@still-studio.com</strong>.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>